high_descs: Turn around and walk to the large wooden table on the right.
Pick up the large brown statue from the middle of the table.
Turn around, take a left, hang a right at the door and walk to the wooden coffee table on the right.
Place the statue on the right side of the coffee table to the right of the laptop computer.
anns.task_desc: Place a statue on a table.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the table with chairs
Pick up the statue from the center of the table
Turn around, go to the coffee table in front of the couch
Put the statue on the table next to the laptop
anns.task_desc: Place a statue on a table with a laptop

high_descs: Turn around and walk around the left side of the table. Then face it.
Pick up the sculpture on the table.
Turn right and walk ahead, then right again, veering right to the coffee table.
Place the sculpture on the coffee table ahead and to the right of the laptop.
anns.task_desc: Place a sculpture on a coffee table.
